# --description--

Sada kada ste izračunali trošak, morate ga dodati na svoj `running_total` da biste pronašli konačan iznos računa.

Koristite operater `+=` da dodate vrednost `tip`-a na svoj `running_total`. Na kraju, koristite `print()` da prikažete niz (string) `Total with tip:` praćen razmakom i vrednošću `running_total`.

# --hints--

You should use the `+=` operator to add the value of `tip` to your `running_total`.

```js
({
    test: () => assert(runPython(`
    _Node(_code).has_stmt('running_total += tip')
    `))
})
```

You should print the string `Total with tip:` followed by a space and the `running_total` variable.

```js
({
    test: () => runPython(`
import io, contextlib, re

buffer = io.StringIO()
with contextlib.redirect_stdout(buffer):
    exec(_code)

match = re.search(r"Total with tip: ([0-9]+(?:\\.[0-9]+)?)", buffer.getvalue())

assert match
assert abs(float(match.group(1)) - ((37.89 + 57.34 + 39.39 + 64.21) * 1.25)) < 1e-6
    `)
})
```

